{
  "category_id": "mascaras_laringeas",
  "name": "Máscaras laríngeas y faciales de vía aérea",
  "schema_version": "0.1.0-draft",
  "status": "draft",
  "base_unit": "unidad (1 mascara laringea)",
  "curation_log": [
    "DRAFT generated by the LLM strawman (design §3 step 5) from real corpus samples — cheap and disposable, never authoritative. Requires the full M1 procedure (mining passes, price-discrimination test, expert curation, reference validation) before launch.",
    "Dry run on 50 corpus samples: coverage {'talla': 0.92, 'tipo': 0.3, 'reutilizable': 0.24, 'material': 0.08, 'esteril': 0.14}, illegal extractions 0."
  ],
  "attribute_defs": [
    {
      "name": "talla",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "n0",
        "n0_5",
        "n1",
        "n1_5",
        "n2",
        "n2_5",
        "n3",
        "n3_5",
        "n4",
        "n4_5",
        "n5",
        "n6",
        "n7"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*0\\.5\\b",
          "value": "n0_5"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b(?:n(?:umero)?|reusable)\\s*1\\.5\\b",
          "value": "n1_5"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*2\\.5\\b",
          "value": "n2_5"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*3\\.5\\b",
          "value": "n3_5"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b(?:n(?:umero)?|reusable)\\s*4\\.5\\b",
          "value": "n4_5"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*0\\b",
          "value": "n0"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*1\\b",
          "value": "n1"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*2\\b",
          "value": "n2"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*3\\b",
          "value": "n3"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*4\\b",
          "value": "n4"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*5\\b",
          "value": "n5"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*6\\b",
          "value": "n6"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bn(?:umero)?\\s*7\\b",
          "value": "n7"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "Identity: el numero de talla es el discriminador principal entre mascaras laringeas; medias tallas y variantes 'reusable X.5' (air q) mapeadas al mismo canonico; reglas de medias tallas y reusable antes que enteros para evitar que 'n 1' capture 'n 1.5'."
    },
    {
      "name": "tipo",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "clasica",
        "proseal",
        "fastrach",
        "air_q",
        "supreme",
        "i_gel"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bfastrach\\b",
          "value": "fastrach"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bproseal\\b",
          "value": "proseal"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bair\\s*q\\b",
          "value": "air_q"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bi\\s*gel\\b",
          "value": "i_gel"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bsupreme\\b",
          "value": "supreme"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bclass?ica?\\b",
          "value": "clasica"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "Identity: el modelo/tipo de mascara (fastrach intubacion, proseal, air q, i gel, supreme, clasica) define productos funcionalmente distintos; air_q antes que clasica porque 'air q classic' contiene ambos terminos."
    },
    {
      "name": "reutilizable",
      "role": "identity",
      "domain": [
        "desechable",
        "reutilizable"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bdesechable\\b",
          "value": "desechable"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b(?:reusable|reutilizable)\\b",
          "value": "reutilizable"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "Identity: desechable vs reutilizable distingue SKUs distintos (un solo uso vs reuso esterilizable); valor ausente en descripciones genericas."
    },
    {
      "name": "material",
      "role": "descriptive",
      "domain": [
        "silicona",
        "pvc"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bsilicona\\b",
          "value": "silicona"
        },
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\bpvc\\b",
          "value": "pvc"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "Descriptive: el material (silicona, pvc) se normaliza pero raramente discrimina identidad frente a talla/tipo; 'libre de latex' es propiedad transversal y se omite."
    },
    {
      "name": "esteril",
      "role": "descriptive",
      "domain": [
        "esteril"
      ],
      "rules": [
        {
          "kind": "keyword",
          "pattern": "\\b(?:esteril|steril)\\b",
          "value": "esteril"
        }
      ],
      "curation_notes": "Descriptive: la esterilidad se normaliza (incluye typo 'steril') pero no participa en la igualdad; casi todas las mascaras son esteriles."
    }
  ]
}